{"snp5.19:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.19 ","snp5.19:0.2":"Parayananugitigatha ","snp5.19:1.1":"“Parayanamanugayissam, ","snp5.19:1.2":"(iccayasma pingiyo) ","snp5.19:1.3":"Yathaddakkhi tathakkhasi; ","snp5.19:1.4":"Vimalo bhurimedhaso, ","snp5.19:1.5":"Nikkamo nibbano nago; ","snp5.19:1.6":"Kissa hetu musa bhane. ","snp5.19:2.1":"Pahinamalamohassa, ","snp5.19:2.2":"manamakkhappahayino; ","snp5.19:2.3":"Handaham kittayissami, ","snp5.19:2.4":"giram vannupasanhitam. ","snp5.19:3.1":"Tamonudo buddho samantacakkhu, ","snp5.19:3.2":"Lokantagu sabbabhavativatto; ","snp5.19:3.3":"Anasavo sabbadukkhappahino, ","snp5.19:3.4":"Saccavhayo brahme upasito me. ","snp5.19:4.1":"Dijo yatha kubbanakam pahaya, ","snp5.19:4.2":"Bahupphalam kananamavaseyya; ","snp5.19:4.3":"Evampaham appadasse pahaya, ","snp5.19:4.4":"Mahodadhim hamsoriva ajjhapatto. ","snp5.19:5.1":"Ye me pubbe viyakamsu, ","snp5.19:5.2":"Huram gotamasasana; ","snp5.19:5.3":"Iccasi iti bhavissati, ","snp5.19:5.4":"Sabbam tam itihitiham; ","snp5.19:5.5":"Sabbam tam takkavaddhanam. ","snp5.19:6.1":"Eko tamanudasino, ","snp5.19:6.2":"jutima so pabhankaro; ","snp5.19:6.3":"Gotamo bhuripannano, ","snp5.19:6.4":"gotamo bhurimedhaso. ","snp5.19:7.1":"Yo me dhammamadesesi, ","snp5.19:7.2":"Sanditthikamakalikam; ","snp5.19:7.3":"Tanhakkhayamanitikam, ","snp5.19:7.4":"Yassa natthi upama kvaci”. ","snp5.19:8.1":"“Kim nu tamha vippavasasi, ","snp5.19:8.2":"muhuttamapi pingiya; ","snp5.19:8.3":"Gotama bhuripannana, ","snp5.19:8.4":"gotama bhurimedhasa. ","snp5.19:9.1":"Yo te dhammamadesesi, ","snp5.19:9.2":"Sanditthikamakalikam; ","snp5.19:9.3":"Tanhakkhayamanitikam, ","snp5.19:9.4":"Yassa natthi upama kvaci”. ","snp5.19:10.1":"“Naham tamha vippavasami, ","snp5.19:10.2":"Muhuttamapi brahmana; ","snp5.19:10.3":"Gotama bhuripannana, ","snp5.19:10.4":"Gotama bhurimedhasa. ","snp5.19:11.1":"Yo me dhammamadesesi, ","snp5.19:11.2":"Sanditthikamakalikam; ","snp5.19:11.3":"Tanhakkhayamanitikam, ","snp5.19:11.4":"Yassa natthi upama kvaci. ","snp5.19:12.1":"Passami nam manasa cakkhunava, ","snp5.19:12.2":"Rattindivam brahmana appamatto; ","snp5.19:12.3":"Namassamano vivasemi rattim, ","snp5.19:12.4":"Teneva mannami avippavasam. ","snp5.19:13.1":"Saddha ca piti ca mano sati ca, ","snp5.19:13.2":"Napentime gotamasasanamha; ","snp5.19:13.3":"Yam yam disam vajati bhuripanno, ","snp5.19:13.4":"Sa tena teneva natohamasmi. ","snp5.19:14.1":"Jinnassa me dubbalathamakassa, ","snp5.19:14.2":"Teneva kayo na paleti tattha; ","snp5.19:14.3":"Sankappayantaya vajami niccam, ","snp5.19:14.4":"Mano hi me brahmana tena yutto. ","snp5.19:15.1":"Panke sayano pariphandamano, ","snp5.19:15.2":"Dipa dipam upaplavim; ","snp5.19:15.3":"Athaddasasim sambuddham, ","snp5.19:15.4":"Oghatinnamanasavam”. ","snp5.19:16.1":"“Yatha ahu vakkali muttasaddho, ","snp5.19:16.2":"Bhadravudho alavigotamo ca; ","snp5.19:16.3":"Evamevam tvampi pamuncassu saddham, ","snp5.19:16.4":"Gamissasi tvam pingiya maccudheyyassa param”. ","snp5.19:17.1":"“Esa bhiyyo pasidami, ","snp5.19:17.2":"Sutvana munino vaco; ","snp5.19:17.3":"Vivattacchado sambuddho, ","snp5.19:17.4":"Akhilo patibhanava. ","snp5.19:18.1":"Adhideve abhinnaya, ","snp5.19:18.2":"Sabbam vedi varovaram; ","snp5.19:18.3":"Panhanantakaro sattha, ","snp5.19:18.4":"Kankhinam patijanatam. ","snp5.19:19.1":"Asamhiram asankuppam, ","snp5.19:19.2":"Yassa natthi upama kvaci; ","snp5.19:19.3":"Addha gamissami na mettha kankha, ","snp5.19:19.4":"Evam mam dharehi adhimuttacittan”ti. ","snp5.19:19.5":"Parayanavaggo pancamo. ","snp5.19:19.6":"Suttuddanam ","snp5.19:20.1":"Urago dhaniyopi ca, ","snp5.19:20.2":"Khaggavisano kasi ca; ","snp5.19:20.3":"Cundo bhavo punadeva, ","snp5.19:20.4":"Vasalo ca karaniyanca; ","snp5.19:20.5":"Hemavato atha yakkho, ","snp5.19:20.6":"Vijayasuttam munisuttavaranti. ","snp5.19:21.1":"Pathamakatthavaro varavaggo, ","snp5.19:21.2":"Dvadasasuttadharo suvibhatto; ","snp5.19:21.3":"Desito cakkhumata vimalena, ","snp5.19:21.4":"Suyyati vaggavaro uragoti. ","snp5.19:22.1":"Ratanamagandho hirimangalanamo, ","snp5.19:22.2":"Sucilomakapilo ca brahmanadhammo; ","snp5.19:22.3":"Nava kimsilautthahano ca, ","snp5.19:22.4":"Rahulo ca punapi vangiso. ","snp5.19:23.1":"Sammaparibbajaniyopi cettha, ","snp5.19:23.2":"Dhammikasuttavaro suvibhatto; ","snp5.19:23.3":"Cuddasasuttadharo dutiyamhi, ","snp5.19:23.4":"Culakavaggavaroti tamahu. ","snp5.19:24.1":"Pabbajjapadhanasubhasitanamo, ","snp5.19:24.2":"Puralaso punadeva magho ca; ","snp5.19:24.3":"Sabhiyam keniyameva sallanamo, ","snp5.19:24.4":"Vasetthavaro kalikopi ca. ","snp5.19:25.1":"Nalakasuttavaro suvibhatto, ","snp5.19:25.2":"Tam anupassi tatha punadeva; ","snp5.19:25.3":"Dvadasasuttadharo tatiyamhi, ","snp5.19:25.4":"Suyyati vaggavaro mahanamo. ","snp5.19:26.1":"Kamaguhatthakadutthakanama, ","snp5.19:26.2":"Suddhavaro paramatthakanamo; ","snp5.19:26.3":"Jara mettiyavaro suvibhatto, ","snp5.19:26.4":"Pasuramagandiya purabhedo. ","snp5.19:27.1":"Kalahavivado ubho viyuha ca, ","snp5.19:27.2":"Tuvatakaattadandasariputta; ","snp5.19:27.3":"Solasasuttadharo catutthamhi, ","snp5.19:27.4":"Atthakavaggavaroti tamahu. ","snp5.19:28.1":"Magadhe janapade ramaniye, ","snp5.19:28.2":"Desavare katapunnanivese; ","snp5.19:28.3":"Pasanakacetiyavare suvibhatte, ","snp5.19:28.4":"Vasi bhagava ganasettho. ","snp5.19:29.1":"Ubhayavasamagatiyamhi, ","snp5.19:29.2":"Dvadasayojaniya parisaya; ","snp5.19:29.3":"Solasabrahmananam kira puttho, ","snp5.19:29.4":"Pucchaya solasapanhakammiya; ","snp5.19:29.5":"Nippakasayi dhammamadasi. ","snp5.19:30.1":"Atthapakasakabyanjanapunnam, ","snp5.19:30.2":"Dhammamadesesi parakhemajaniyam; ","snp5.19:30.3":"Lokahitaya jino dvipadaggo, ","snp5.19:30.4":"Suttavaram bahudhammavicitram; ","snp5.19:30.5":"Sabbakilesapamocanahetum, ","snp5.19:30.6":"Desayi suttavaram dvipadaggo. ","snp5.19:31.1":"Byanjanamatthapadam samayuttam, ","snp5.19:31.2":"Akkharasannitaopamagalham; ","snp5.19:31.3":"Lokavicaranananapabhaggam, ","snp5.19:31.4":"Desayi suttavaram dvipadaggo. ","snp5.19:32.1":"Ragamale amalam vimalaggam, ","snp5.19:32.2":"Dosamale amalam vimalaggam; ","snp5.19:32.3":"Mohamale amalam vimalaggam, ","snp5.19:32.4":"Lokavicaranananapabhaggam; ","snp5.19:32.5":"Desayi suttavaram dvipadaggo. ","snp5.19:33.1":"Klesamale amalam vimalaggam, ","snp5.19:33.2":"Duccaritamale amalam vimalaggam; ","snp5.19:33.3":"Lokavicaranananapabhaggam, ","snp5.19:33.4":"Desayi suttavaram dvipadaggo. ","snp5.19:34.1":"Asavabandhanayogakilesam, ","snp5.19:34.2":"Nivaranani ca tini malani; ","snp5.19:34.3":"Tassa kilesapamocanahetum, ","snp5.19:34.4":"Desayi suttavaram dvipadaggo. ","snp5.19:35.1":"Nimmalasabbakilesapanudam, ","snp5.19:35.2":"Ragaviragamanejamasokam; ","snp5.19:35.3":"Santapanitasududdasadhammam, ","snp5.19:35.4":"Desayi suttavaram dvipadaggo. ","snp5.19:36.1":"Raganca dosakamabhanjitasantam, ","snp5.19:36.2":"Yonicatuggatipancavinnanam; ","snp5.19:36.3":"Tanharatacchadanatanalatapamokkham, ","snp5.19:36.4":"Desayi suttavaram dvipadaggo. ","snp5.19:37.1":"Gambhiraduddasasanhanipunam, ","snp5.19:37.2":"Panditavedaniyam nipunattham; ","snp5.19:37.3":"Lokavicaranananapabhaggam, ","snp5.19:37.4":"Desayi suttavaram dvipadaggo. ","snp5.19:38.1":"Navangakusumamalagiveyyam, ","snp5.19:38.2":"Indriyajhanavimokkhavibhattam; ","snp5.19:38.3":"Atthangamaggadharam varayanam, ","snp5.19:38.4":"Desayi suttavaram dvipadaggo. ","snp5.19:39.1":"Somupamam vimalam parisuddham, ","snp5.19:39.2":"Annavamupamaratanasucittam; ","snp5.19:39.3":"Pupphasamam ravimupamatejam, ","snp5.19:39.4":"Desayi suttavaram dvipadaggo. ","snp5.19:40.1":"Khemasivam sukhasitalasantam, ","snp5.19:40.2":"Maccutatanaparam paramattham; ","snp5.19:40.3":"Tassa sunibbutadassanahetum, ","snp5.19:40.4":"Desayi suttavaram dvipadaggoti. ","snp5.19:40.5":"Suttanipatapali samatta. "}